        "article": "BJP today claimed that the Aam Aadmi Party-led Punjab Government has implemented the Viksit Bharat G Ram G scheme after initially opposing it. Addressing the media in New Delhi, BJP spokesperson Prem Shukla questioned the Punjab Government&#8217;s sudden decision to implement the center&#8217;s rural employment scheme. He alleged that the Bhagwant Mann Government is now praising VB G RAM G",
