        "summary": "Union Finance Minister Nirmala Sitharaman has embarked on a four-day official visit to France today. The Finance Ministry has informed that Ms Sitharaman will participate in a series of high-level bilateral engagements aimed at further strengthening the India-France Strategic Partnership, enhancing economic cooperation and promoting investment, technology collaboration and innovation. She will als",
